```dockerfile
# Stage 1: Build frontend assets
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-builder
LABEL stage="frontend-builder"

WORKDIR /build/frontend

COPY frontend/package.json frontend/package-lock.json ./

RUN npm ci

COPY frontend/ .

RUN npm run build

# Stage 2: Build Python dependencies
FROM python:3.12-slim AS python-builder
LABEL stage="python-builder"

WORKDIR /build

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    build-essential \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir poetry

COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./

RUN poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry install --no-root --no-dev

# Stage 3: Runtime
FROM python:3.12-slim

LABEL maintainer="Superset Team" \
      description="Analytics platform with Python backend and React frontend"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq-dev \
    unixodbc-dev \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN useradd -m -u 1000 -s /bin/bash superset

COPY --from=python-builder /build/.venv /app/.venv
COPY --from=frontend-builder /build/frontend/dist /app/static

COPY app/ /app/app/
COPY config.py /app/

ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH" \
    PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1

RUN chown -R superset:superset /app

USER superset

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
